      "module_path": "agent_profiles",
      "docs": "Serde DTO for a single capability entry in agent-profiles.json. All fields are private; access via accessor methods. timeout_seconds and prompt_template_path are per-capability settings added by T006 (IN-09, CN-07, AC-12) to support the ref-verifier capability's independent timeout and prompt template configuration. Raw primitives are justified: timeout_seconds is a truly opaque u64 tick count with no domain constraint; prompt_template_path is a free-form filesystem path with no domain validation.",
